<i>some magnificent spread.</i>

11:35.569 --> 11:38.364
<i>Something that's</i>
<i>been in the family for--</i>

11:38.364 --> 11:40.991
<i>Well, it was in</i>
<i>the family years ago.</i>

11:41.033 --> 11:42.535
<i>And now, once again.</i>

11:42.535 --> 11:45.162
<i>My great-great-great</i>
<i>-great-grandfather</i>

11:45.204 --> 11:47.498
<i>-built those stone fences...</i>
<i>-Ah.</i>

11:47.540 --> 11:48.666
<i>...and hid behind them,</i>

11:48.708 --> 11:51.043
<i>firing his musket</i>
<i>at the Redcoats.</i>

11:51.085 --> 11:53.254
<i>Hmm. [chuckles]</i>

11:54.380 --> 11:55.464
<i>Yeah.</i>

11:55.506 --> 11:58.050
<i>You'd think</i>
<i>a place this grand,</i>

11:58.092 --> 11:59.719
<i>it would suck up the sound.</i>

11:59.760 --> 12:02.221
<i>But it's a funny thing</i>
<i>about gunpowder and sky,</i>

12:02.221 --> 12:04.598
<i>one offers little</i>
<i>resistance to the other.</i>

12:04.640 --> 12:05.808
<i>That's the thing</i>
<i>about a cannon,</i>

12:05.808 --> 12:08.352
<i>nothing much</i>
<i>offers it resistance.</i>

12:08.352 --> 12:09.520
<i>[laughs]</i>

12:09.520 --> 12:12.732
<i>That's why I have such</i>
<i>regard for their power.</i>

12:13.566 --> 12:16.110
<i>Well, that's why I'm here.</i>

12:16.110 --> 12:17.194
<i>The artillery.</i>

12:17.236 --> 12:19.822
<i>For one thing, uh,</i>
<i>we share a stream,</i>

12:19.822 --> 12:21.782
<i>that I irrigate my fields with,</i>

12:21.824 --> 12:24.368
<i>and when it comes</i>
<i>to black powder residue</i>

12:24.368 --> 12:25.703
<i>and leaching metals--</i>

12:25.703 --> 12:28.330
<i>I'm downstream of you.</i>

12:28.372 --> 12:29.248
<i>Mm-hmm.</i>

12:29.290 --> 12:31.208
<i>-So you are.</i>
<i>-Hmm-hmm.</i>

12:31.250 --> 12:33.419
<i>Then there's the noise.</i>

12:33.461 --> 12:36.088
<i>It's really jarring</i>
<i>and unsettling.</i>

12:36.130 --> 12:37.965
<i>And I'm not a dairy outfit,</i>

12:38.007 --> 12:40.551
<i>but I do have a milk cow,</i>
<i>and she's sensitive.</i>

12:40.551 --> 12:44.096
<i>She won't give milk with all</i>
<i>the bombs bursting in air.</i>

12:44.138 --> 12:46.515
<i>Well, I'm sorry to hear your</i>
<i>Guernsey's teats are swoll--</i>

12:46.557 --> 12:48.225
<i>She's a Holstein.</i>

12:48.225 --> 12:50.478
<i>That's--</i>

12:50.478 --> 12:53.939
<i>[sighs] A smart man once said,</i>

12:53.939 --> 12:56.442
<i>"Nothing external</i>
<i>affects how you feel.</i>

12:56.442 --> 12:58.986
<i>You control how you feel."</i>

12:59.528 --> 13:00.613
<i>So I say this,</i>

13:00.654 --> 13:02.656
<i>"When you hear</i>
<i>the sound of the cannon,</i>

13:02.656 --> 13:04.241
<i>why don't you hear what I do?"</i>

13:04.241 --> 13:06.118
<i>The sound of liberty,</i>

13:06.160 --> 13:08.287
<i>of triumph.</i>

13:08.329 --> 13:09.497
<i>Of America!</i>

13:09.497 --> 13:11.916
<i>You can make yourself</i>
<i>process it that way.</i>

13:11.957 --> 13:13.542
<i>Hmm.</i>

13:13.584 --> 13:16.462
<i>Seems like an awful</i>
<i>lot of work.</i>

13:16.504 --> 13:18.589
<i>[sighs] Work...</i>

13:18.631 --> 13:20.716
<i>is how I made the fortune</i>

13:20.758 --> 13:23.511
<i>that's allowed me</i>
<i>to possess this place anew.</i>

13:23.552 --> 13:24.929
<i>Work is what men like me...</i>

13:24.970 --> 13:27.556
<i>And, I assume, you,</i>
<i>are made of.</i>

13:27.556 --> 13:31.477
<i>Sure. No, I'm familiar with</i>
<i>the bromides of the self-made.</i>

13:31.519 --> 13:34.772
<i>The work-is-the-tonic types.</i>

13:34.814 --> 13:36.565
<i>Perhaps you could do me</i>
<i>the courtesy</i>

13:36.565 --> 13:39.318
<i>of just limiting</i>
<i>the number of times a week.</i>

13:39.318 --> 13:41.320
<i>It's strictly limited.</i>

13:41.320 --> 13:42.947
<i>Morning and nightfall.</i>

13:42.947 --> 13:44.824
<i>-I'm a constitutional scholar...</i>
<i>-Ah.</i>

13:44.865 --> 13:47.576
<i>Not as a vocation, like you,</i>

13:47.618 --> 13:48.869
<i>but as an avocation.</i>

13:48.911 --> 13:51.413
<i>And the amendments</i>
<i>to that vaunted document--</i>

13:51.455 --> 13:52.957
<i>[chuckles]</i>
<i>Oh, I'm ahead of you.</i>

13:52.957 --> 13:56.544
<i>Yes, I know which amendment</i>
<i>you're so keen on.</i>

13:58.379 --> 13:59.672
<i>Well, thanks for the visit.</i>

13:59.713 --> 14:02.591
<i>Mind Mr. Frost's words</i>
<i>about good fences.</i>

14:02.633 --> 14:04.426
<i>Ah, the neighbors</i>
<i>worked together</i>

14:04.468 --> 14:06.178
<i>in Robert Frost's</i>
<i>"Mending Wall."</i>

14:06.178 --> 14:07.638
<i>The point is wholly--</i>

14:07.680 --> 14:09.223
<i>Whatever.</i>

14:09.223 --> 14:10.432
<i>[chuckles]</i>

14:10.474 --> 14:12.142
<i>I didn't come</i>
<i>looking for a war.</i>

14:12.184 --> 14:14.520
<i>Well I, on the other hand,</i>
<i>have always regretted</i>

14:14.520 --> 14:17.022
<i>I didn't get a chance</i>
<i>to fight in mine.</i>

14:17.022 --> 14:18.482
<i>[scoffs]</i>

14:35.040 --> 14:37.167
<i>Former culture wasn't</i>
<i>a problem for me.</i>

14:37.209 --> 14:39.837
<i>New one won't be either.</i>
<i>I'm not like these weak-knees.</i>

14:39.879 --> 14:41.839
<i>You're not talking</i>
<i>about me, are you?</i>

14:41.839 --> 14:43.674
<i>I hope you don't think</i>
<i>my knees are weak, they're--</i>

14:43.674 --> 14:45.759
<i>Well, he's not fucking</i>
<i>talking about me, dude.</i>

14:45.801 --> 14:47.678
<i>[Prince]</i>
<i>Let's start with this.</i>

14:47.678 --> 14:50.139
<i>There's no shame</i>
<i>in being sensitive.</i>

14:50.180 --> 14:51.473
<i>You need to be.</i>

14:51.473 --> 14:53.142
<i>One of the secrets</i>
<i>to being a great investor</i>

14:53.183 --> 14:55.477
<i>is recognizing the impulses</i>
<i>that might lead you</i>

14:55.519 --> 14:57.229
<i>to make decisions</i>
<i>based on emotion.</i>

14:57.271 --> 14:59.857
<i>If you're not training yourself</i>
<i>to recognize those,</i>

14:59.857 --> 15:02.067
<i>your subconscious will</i>
<i>just be directed by them.</i>

15:02.067 --> 15:02.985
<i>Thank you!</i>

15:03.027 --> 15:04.570
<i>Now you won't have</i>
<i>to go the bathroom</i>

15:04.570 --> 15:05.529
<i>when you want to cry, Tuk.</i>

15:05.571 --> 15:06.906
<i>Once! One time and--</i>

15:06.906 --> 15:08.949
<i>What was encouraged</i>
<i>was more of a</i>

15:08.991 --> 15:11.160
<i>"Stick your emotions</i>
<i>where your conscience is,</i>

15:11.160 --> 15:14.246
<i>and then tie 'em off</i>
<i>like a gangrenous leg</i>

15:14.246 --> 15:16.457
<i>until they wither and die.</i>

15:16.498 --> 15:18.375
<i>Then chop 'em off forever."</i>

15:18.375 --> 15:19.752
<i>What effect do</i>
<i>you think that had?</i>

15:19.752 --> 15:21.086
<i>Greased the way to profit.</i>

15:21.086 --> 15:23.839
<i>Take the friction out.</i>
<i>For guys like me and Bonnie.</i>

15:23.839 --> 15:26.425
<i>And led to some pretty</i>
<i>close calls with the SEC,</i>

15:26.425 --> 15:27.760
<i>the U.S. Attorney's Office,</i>
<i>the--</i>

15:27.760 --> 15:29.011
<i>Never convicted!</i>
<i>We were--</i>

15:29.053 --> 15:31.055
<i>I mean, Axe was, sort of,</i>
<i>in absentia.</i>

15:31.096 --> 15:33.223
<i>We're going on a different</i>
<i>kind of exploration here.</i>

15:33.223 --> 15:35.893
<i>Because I believe it'll</i>
<i>lead you to be better,</i>

15:35.893 --> 15:38.228
<i>not worse, at your jobs.</i>

15:40.689 --> 15:42.858
<i>We used to work for a killer,</i>

15:42.900 --> 15:45.736
<i>now we've got a guy who wants</i>
<i>to know how we "feel."</i>

15:45.778 --> 15:48.447
<i>Why is he asking</i>
<i>for our guidance?</i>

15:48.489 --> 15:49.698
<i>Why doesn't he</i>
<i>know what to do?</i>

15:49.740 --> 15:51.408
<i>Point me at a hill,</i>

15:51.450 --> 15:52.785
<i>tell me to take the hill.</i>

15:52.785 --> 15:54.078
<i>That's what I want in a general.</i>

15:54.078 --> 15:57.748
<i>I must admit, Axe's</i>
<i>ruthlessness was almost...</i>

15:57.790 --> 15:59.959
<i>reassuring.</i>

16:01.335 --> 16:02.753
<i>This might not be salvageable.</i>

16:02.795 --> 16:05.255
<i>Maybe we just take</i>
<i>the joint down to the rivets.</i>

16:05.297 --> 16:06.382
<i>Start over.</i>

16:06.423 --> 16:07.299
<i>Nah.</i>

16:07.299 --> 16:09.468
<i>We can turn it around.</i>

16:09.510 --> 16:11.220
<i>Can't we?</i>

16:11.261 --> 16:13.097
<i>Turn it around?</i>

16:13.097 --> 16:14.056
<i>Can you?</i>

16:14.098 --> 16:17.643
<i>Well, if anyone can</i>
<i>guide me there, it's you.</i>

16:17.685 --> 16:20.980
<i>You're the magic sauce,</i>
<i>aren't you?</i>

16:20.980 --> 16:23.691
<i>Special sauce.</i>
<i>Magic touch.</i>

16:23.732 --> 16:25.693
<i>I don't get nervous.</i>
<i>You make me nervous.</i>

16:25.734 --> 16:27.194
<i>Like you can see through me.</i>

16:27.236 --> 16:29.780
<i>That's a good technique.</i>
<i>But you're not nervous.</i>

16:29.780 --> 16:31.031
<i>And you said</i>
<i>"magic sauce" on purpose</i>

16:31.073 --> 16:34.368
<i>to give me the power</i>
<i>in the conversation.</i>

16:35.536 --> 16:37.871
<i>What do you want with me?</i>

16:37.913 --> 16:40.207
<i>I wanted to see if you were</i>
<i>that good. You are.</i>

16:40.207 --> 16:42.626
<i>That's very much up</i>
<i>for debate right now.</i>

16:42.668 --> 16:43.961
<i>Not with me.</i>

16:43.961 --> 16:45.337
<i>I look at my results,</i>

16:45.379 --> 16:47.715
<i>and I don't see a lot of</i>
<i>checkmarks in the win column.</i>

16:47.715 --> 16:49.842
<i>My guy lost this whole place.</i>

16:49.883 --> 16:51.760
<i>Guy hits 700 home runs,</i>

16:51.802 --> 16:53.721
<i>but gets caught bringing</i>
<i>a corked bat to plate,</i>

16:53.762 --> 16:56.306
<i>you can't blame yourself</i>
<i>without also taking credit</i>

16:56.348 --> 16:57.641
<i>for the 700 dingers.</i>

16:57.683 --> 16:59.309
<i>The one matters</i>
<i>more than the other.</i>

16:59.309 --> 17:00.728
<i>On that, we agree.</i>

17:00.769 --> 17:03.355
<i>You'll find no pine tar,</i>
<i>no cork,</i>

17:03.397 --> 17:04.982
<i>no dented garbage cans,</i>

17:04.982 --> 17:06.483
<i>no signs stolen here.</i>

17:06.483 --> 17:08.027
<i>Okay, Mr. October.</i>

17:08.068 --> 17:09.194
<i>But I'm not settling either,</i>

17:09.236 --> 17:10.988
<i>for my current</i>
<i>level of performance.</i>

17:11.030 --> 17:13.490
<i>And here's one</i>
<i>you probably didn't guess.</i>

17:13.490 --> 17:14.950
<i>I've never been coached.</i>

17:14.992 --> 17:18.037
<i>Not since</i>
<i>I was an athlete, I mean.</i>

17:18.037 --> 17:20.039
<i>No therapy,</i>
<i>no executive coaching,</i>

17:20.039 --> 17:22.332
<i>no shrink, no life guru.</i>

17:22.916 --> 17:23.917
<i>But with you--</i>

17:23.959 --> 17:26.503
<i>Nah, there is no "with me."</i>

17:27.588 --> 17:30.090
<i>If I can somehow</i>
<i>still do what I used to,</i>

17:30.090 --> 17:32.593
<i>I can't do it</i>
<i>with someone unless I have,</i>

17:32.593 --> 17:34.470
<i>or can manufacture, objectivity.</i>

17:34.511 --> 17:36.722
<i>You weren't</i>
<i>objective about Axe.</i>

17:36.764 --> 17:38.640
<i>[scoffs] Yeah,</i>
<i>not so hype about his name</i>

17:38.682 --> 17:41.643
<i>coming out of your mouth.</i>
<i>There's no need for that.</i>

17:41.685 --> 17:43.937
<i>And how I felt about him</i>
<i>has nothing to do with</i>

17:43.937 --> 17:46.190
<i>how I feel about you. I...</i>

17:46.190 --> 17:47.858
<i>well, I didn't</i>
<i>resent or hate him.</i>

17:47.900 --> 17:50.152
<i>Hate? Ouch.</i>
<i>Hate feels extreme.</i>

17:50.194 --> 17:52.071
<i>How else should</i>
<i>your prisoners think of you?</i>

17:52.071 --> 17:53.572
<i>You're not a prisoner.</i>

17:53.572 --> 17:55.407
<i>You signed</i>
<i>an employment contract.</i>

17:55.407 --> 17:57.826
<i>So did a certain musical genius</i>
<i>you share a name with.</i>

17:57.868 --> 18:00.662
<i>Didn't stop him from writing</i>
<i>"slave" on his face.</i>

18:00.704 --> 18:02.081
<i>Technically,</i>
<i>once he did that,</i>

18:02.122 --> 18:03.957
<i>he was The Artist</i>
<i>Formerly Known as Prince.</i>

18:03.999 --> 18:05.918
<i>And, look,</i>
<i>I bargained for your services,</i>

18:05.918 --> 18:07.711
<i>but I would never keep</i>
<i>you here against your will.</i>

18:07.711 --> 18:09.922
<i>So I can leave</i>
<i>and work at another fund?</i>

18:09.922 --> 18:11.799
<i>Oh, we're not there yet.</i>
<i>You leaving?</i>

18:11.840 --> 18:14.426
<i>We're still getting</i>
<i>to know each other.</i>

18:17.971 --> 18:19.598
<i>Investors are clamoring</i>
<i>for a meeting.</i>

18:19.640 --> 18:21.225
<i>-Which ones?</i>
<i>-All of 'em.</i>

18:21.225 --> 18:23.602
<i>I'm holding them at bay,</i>
<i>but you've got to give them</i>

18:23.602 --> 18:24.978
<i>the new manifesto</i>
<i>by the end of the week</i>

18:24.978 --> 18:27.898
<i>or they're going to peel off.</i>
<i>En masse.</i>

18:27.898 --> 18:29.775
<i>Should we sound him</i>
<i>out about it?</i>

18:29.817 --> 18:32.027
<i>I just don't see</i>
<i>the point.</i>

18:32.027 --> 18:34.113
<i>So you've said, but</i>
<i>the institutional knowledge--</i>

18:34.113 --> 18:36.824
<i>So you've said.</i>
<i>But isn't he someone who's</i>

18:36.824 --> 18:38.367
<i>stuck around too long, like...</i>

18:38.367 --> 18:39.785
<i>Hit me with a ref.</i>

18:39.827 --> 18:42.079
<i>Like Jan-Michael Vincent</i>
<i>in</i> <i>Hangfire.</i>

18:42.121 --> 18:43.205
<i>I'll have to trust you.</i>

18:43.247 --> 18:44.915
<i>Believe me,</i>
<i>it wasn't pretty.</i>

18:44.957 --> 18:46.917
<i>Even if I wanted</i>
<i>to get rid of him,</i>

18:46.959 --> 18:48.460
<i>-the buyout makes it--</i>
<i>-Popping a zit</i>

18:48.502 --> 18:50.462
<i>is painful for a moment.</i>
<i>But then, you're blemish-free.</i>

18:50.462 --> 18:52.965
<i>Yeah. If it cost me</i>
<i>80 million bucks to pop a zit.</i>

18:52.965 --> 18:54.842
<i>You sound a little sorry</i>
<i>we made the call.</i>

18:54.842 --> 18:56.552
<i>-So we make him want to quit?</i>
<i>-He has to.</i>

18:56.593 --> 18:59.847
<i>Or has to get fired for cause</i>
<i>for us to get out of the deal.</i>

18:59.888 --> 19:02.141
<i>He'll get the idea</i>
<i>without us doing anything,</i>

19:02.182 --> 19:04.977
<i>as soon as he sees he has</i>
<i>no influence here anymore,</i>

19:04.977 --> 19:07.771
<i>no portfolio, no life.</i>

19:17.489 --> 19:19.199
<i>Why do you want to give me</i>
<i>this only to take it back</i>

19:19.199 --> 19:21.118
<i>after you fire me</i>
<i>at the end of the day</i>

19:21.118 --> 19:23.745
<i>or week or whenever it is</i>
<i>in your calendar for?</i>

19:23.787 --> 19:25.914
<i>There's no date for that</i>
<i>in the calendar right now.</i>

19:25.914 --> 19:27.749
<i>Your institutional knowledge--</i>

19:27.791 --> 19:29.710
<i>If you shitcan me before</i>
<i>you hear everyone out,</i>

19:29.710 --> 19:31.253
<i>you think there'll be a revolt.</i>

19:31.253 --> 19:33.839
<i>-We aren't rushing anything.</i>
<i>-Uh-huh.</i>

19:33.839 --> 19:35.591
<i>When do we charge this puppy?</i>

19:35.591 --> 19:36.717
<i>Self-charging.</i>

19:36.758 --> 19:37.843
<i>You wear it 24/7.</i>

19:37.843 --> 19:40.387
<i>To bed. When you work out.</i>

19:53.233 --> 19:55.819
<i>They put drones</i>
<i>on our fingers, people,</i>

19:55.819 --> 19:57.487
<i>to watch our every move.</i>

19:57.487 --> 19:59.698
<i>Grip 'em and rip 'em!</i>

19:59.698 --> 20:01.283
<i>It's always</i>
<i>the fucking nice guys.</i>

20:01.283 --> 20:02.951
<i>Is there GPS</i>
<i>on this thing too?</i>

20:02.993 --> 20:04.453
<i>I like the ring,</i>
<i>but not how he did it.</i>

20:04.494 --> 20:07.122
<i>Invasion of goddamned privacy</i>
<i>is what it is.</i>

20:07.122 --> 20:08.290
<i>Spying on us?</i>

20:08.332 --> 20:10.500
<i>We can't have</i>
<i>invaded your privacy.</i>

20:10.500 --> 20:11.835
<i>You invited us in.</i>

20:11.877 --> 20:13.170
<i>Each of you gave permission</i>
<i>when you launched the app</i>

20:13.170 --> 20:14.713
<i>and clicked agree.</i>

20:14.713 --> 20:16.131
<i>Everyone always</i>
<i>just clicks agree.</i>

20:16.131 --> 20:18.508
<i>-You tricked us!</i>
<i>-[Taylor] Not everyone, Tuk.</i>

20:18.550 --> 20:21.136
<i>I put mine on my dog's collar</i>
<i>the night we got 'em.</i>

20:21.178 --> 20:23.138
<i>[Rian] I paid a marathoner</i>
<i>friend of mine to wear it.</i>

20:23.138 --> 20:26.308
<i>-Forty-four BPM, baby!</i>
<i>-You should've told us.</i>

20:26.350 --> 20:29.853
<i>Those tech geeks only</i>
<i>care about themselves.</i>

20:29.895 --> 20:30.938
<i>Not even.</i>

20:30.938 --> 20:33.440
<i>It's each for his own</i>
<i>from here on out.</i>

20:37.236 --> 20:38.987
<i>Shouldn't you get</i>
<i>in the middle of this?</i>

20:39.029 --> 20:41.949
<i>it's good for them</i>
<i>to let it out.</i>

20:48.956 --> 20:49.873
<i>[sighs]</i>

20:49.915 --> 20:51.792
<i>-[knocks]</i>
<i>-Hello?</i>

20:51.833 --> 20:53.502
<i>[Mayor] Come on in.</i>

20:53.502 --> 20:54.670
<i>Mr. Mayor, I'm--</i>

20:54.711 --> 20:56.046
<i>I know who you are.</i>

20:56.088 --> 20:58.799
<i>Word went around when you</i>
<i>bought your land for your...</i>

20:58.840 --> 20:59.925
<i>sabbatical.</i>

20:59.925 --> 21:01.009
<i>[laughs]</i>

21:01.051 --> 21:02.261
<i>Not a sabbatical.</i>

21:02.261 --> 21:03.762
<i>Just... still the AG.</i>

21:03.762 --> 21:06.139
<i>Just working from</i>
<i>the farm for a while.</i>

21:06.181 --> 21:07.975
<i>The air out here, you know?</i>

21:08.016 --> 21:09.142
<i>The clarity.</i>

21:09.184 --> 21:12.312
<i>What matters becomes clear.</i>

21:12.312 --> 21:14.564
<i>What are you working on there,</i>
<i>a buck tail?</i>

21:14.564 --> 21:15.440
<i>Moose May.</i>

21:15.482 --> 21:17.567
<i>Blackfly season's</i>
<i>brutal around here.</i>

21:17.567 --> 21:20.988
<i>Least I can do is</i>
<i>land some trout thanks to 'em.</i>

21:20.988 --> 21:22.739
<i>[chuckles]</i>

21:23.573 --> 21:25.575
<i>Mr. Mayor,</i>

21:25.617 --> 21:29.579
<i>how is it a resident</i>
<i>can fire off military-grade,</i>

21:29.621 --> 21:31.123
<i>albeit antique, weaponry?</i>

21:31.164 --> 21:34.084
<i>Ah, you're talking</i>
<i>about Melville Revere,</i>

21:34.084 --> 21:36.420
<i>a prominent</i>
<i>and beloved resident.</i>

21:36.461 --> 21:40.007
<i>Well, having commemorative</i>
<i>cannonry isn't a violation</i>

21:40.007 --> 21:41.842
<i>of the National Firearms Act.</i>

21:41.842 --> 21:43.427
<i>It is if it's operational.</i>

21:43.468 --> 21:46.305
<i>Well, he also has</i>
<i>a state firearms license.</i>

21:46.305 --> 21:48.890
<i>He's a wealthy man</i>
<i>with lots of lawyers</i>

21:48.890 --> 21:51.560
<i>and "friends in high places,"</i>
<i>as they say.</i>

21:51.601 --> 21:56.315
<i>And he has a special waiver</i>
<i>from the ATF to use them.</i>

21:56.315 --> 21:59.693
<i>Imagine a private citizen</i>
<i>with all that.</i>

21:59.693 --> 22:01.361
<i>Mr. Rhoades, you should know,</i>

22:01.361 --> 22:03.238
<i>Stony Gorge is a quiet hamlet.</i>

22:03.238 --> 22:06.658
<i>It'd be a hell of a lot quieter</i>
<i>without all that ordnance.</i>

22:07.200 --> 22:09.536
<i>We mind our own business here.</i>

22:10.203 --> 22:12.789
<i>Town has learned</i>
<i>to live with it.</i>

22:12.789 --> 22:14.958
<i>I suggest you do too.</i>

22:17.669 --> 22:19.880
<i>[snipping]</i>

22:46.239 --> 22:48.909
<i>Allow me to stand a round</i>
<i>of John Barleycorn</i>

22:48.950 --> 22:50.744
<i>for my new friends</i>
<i>and neighbors.</i>

22:50.786 --> 22:52.662
<i>-[man] Hear, hear.</i>
<i>-Thanks.</i>

22:52.662 --> 22:54.373
<i>Hmm-hmm.</i>

22:55.999 --> 22:57.751
<i>Great.</i>

23:04.091 --> 23:06.635
<i>[exhales]</i>

23:06.676 --> 23:08.512
<i>[soft chuckles]</i>

23:09.262 --> 23:10.597
<i>Is it just me,</i>

23:10.597 --> 23:13.141
<i>or does it feel like</i>
<i>we're living in a war zone</i>

23:13.141 --> 23:15.769
<i>around here at dawn and dusk?</i>

23:20.899 --> 23:22.734
<i>Ah. I guess he's, uh,</i>

23:22.734 --> 23:24.403
<i>one of your own,</i>

23:24.403 --> 23:26.154
<i>so you hold him close.</i>

23:26.196 --> 23:28.240
<i>What he is,</i>
<i>is a stuck-up prick.</i>

23:28.281 --> 23:29.658
<i>[all laugh]</i>

23:29.658 --> 23:30.951
<i>Well, I know this:</i>

23:30.951 --> 23:33.120
<i>If anyone else was</i>
<i>firing field artillery,</i>

23:33.120 --> 23:34.913
<i>he'd be locked up.</i>

23:34.913 --> 23:36.373
<i>So how's he getting a free pass?</i>

23:36.415 --> 23:40.377
<i>Fire department needed</i>
<i>a new ladder truck last year.</i>

23:40.419 --> 23:41.670
<i>Guess who bought it?</i>

23:41.670 --> 23:43.588
<i>Police department</i>
<i>needs new gear, he ponies up.</i>

23:43.588 --> 23:46.341
<i>-Same with the Little League.</i>
<i>-And with the Boy Scouts.</i>

23:46.383 --> 23:48.301
<i>No one will</i>
<i>line up against him.</i>

23:48.343 --> 23:49.511
<i>It's too dangerous.</i>

23:49.553 --> 23:51.805
<i>-And could cost too much.</i>
<i>-Hmm-hmm.</i>

23:51.847 --> 23:54.766
<i>So he's buying indulgences.</i>

23:54.766 --> 23:56.643
<i>Yeah, but he pays in cash.</i>

23:57.769 --> 23:59.104
<i>[scoffs]</i>

24:06.486 --> 24:08.864
<i>I'd really love Chuck</i>
<i>to have a look at my opening.</i>

24:08.905 --> 24:10.073
<i>I'll take a look at it.</i>

24:10.073 --> 24:12.284
<i>My judge, he</i>
<i>worked for Chuck. Can he--</i>

24:12.284 --> 24:14.286
<i>I know him from Southern.</i>
<i>I'll touch base.</i>

24:14.286 --> 24:16.746
<i>I'm handling all matters, Chuck.</i>

24:21.626 --> 24:23.170
<i>[sighs]</i>

24:25.046 --> 24:27.132
<i>Okay. Now I need to do</i>
<i>some real listening.</i>

24:27.174 --> 24:29.384
<i>To you. Bottom-line it.</i>

24:29.384 --> 24:30.886
<i>Biggest issue.</i>

24:30.886 --> 24:32.387
<i>You have investors who are wary.</i>

24:32.387 --> 24:35.098
<i>You're a long-hold player in</i>
<i>a high-vol game all of a sudden.</i>

24:35.140 --> 24:36.641
<i>They'll get more</i>
<i>and more restless</i>

24:36.683 --> 24:38.977
<i>as you find your footing</i>
<i>in this hedge fund landscape.</i>

24:39.019 --> 24:40.187
<i>In order to keep</i>
<i>the investors,</i>

24:40.187 --> 24:41.313
<i>we need to win the employees.</i>

24:41.313 --> 24:43.064
<i>Right. Which, I think,</i>
<i>is in motion</i>

24:43.106 --> 24:45.108
<i>to the extent that</i>
<i>we know how to reach them.</i>

24:45.108 --> 24:47.110
<i>But neither of us yet have</i>
<i>rhythm with this bunch.</i>

24:47.152 --> 24:48.528
<i>Not our kind of folks,</i>
<i>on the face of it.</i>

24:48.570 --> 24:50.697
<i>-But in this game--</i>
<i>-They are the best.</i>

24:50.697 --> 24:52.949
<i>Which is what</i>
<i>the investors count on.</i>

24:52.949 --> 24:54.201
<i>But the way</i>
<i>they've always done it</i>

24:54.201 --> 24:55.660
<i>puts us at risk going forward.</i>

24:55.660 --> 24:58.914
<i>As discussed, we won't</i>
<i>allow that stuff to happen.</i>

24:58.914 --> 25:00.040
<i>Correct.</i>

25:00.081 --> 25:01.500
<i>And I've tasked the back</i>
<i>office with yanking out</i>

25:01.541 --> 25:03.668
<i>the odd remaining bad tooth</i>
<i>to turn over to the SEC</i>

25:03.668 --> 25:06.087
<i>so the new company</i>
<i>can start fresh</i>

25:06.129 --> 25:07.172
<i>and with trust.</i>

25:07.172 --> 25:08.423
<i>Because the place as-is,</i>

25:08.465 --> 25:10.675
<i>the Commission's</i>
<i>not gonna like it.</i>

25:13.178 --> 25:15.847
<i>Speaking of bad teeth.</i>

25:18.016 --> 25:20.810
<i>We need a full</i>
<i>compliance report.</i>

25:22.020 --> 25:23.813
<i>Can do.</i>

25:23.813 --> 25:26.900
<i>But once I hand it over,</i>

25:26.900 --> 25:29.694
<i>you're in it, responsible.</i>

25:29.694 --> 25:30.445
<i>[laughs]</i>

25:30.445 --> 25:31.988
<i>That's how it has to be.</i>

25:32.030 --> 25:33.406
<i>What's this?</i>

25:33.448 --> 25:36.576
<i>This is a little filing system</i>
<i>that I've just implemented</i>

25:36.576 --> 25:37.827
<i>to separate out our trades</i>

25:37.869 --> 25:41.498
<i>based on how far over</i>
<i>the line of securities law</i>

25:41.498 --> 25:42.624
<i>each transaction was.</i>

25:42.624 --> 25:45.252
<i>You know</i>
<i>we need a little red meat</i>

25:45.293 --> 25:46.419
<i>to throw the SEC,</i>

25:46.419 --> 25:48.338
<i>something so they know</i>
<i>we're committed</i>

25:48.380 --> 25:50.549
<i>to being a clean operation.</i>

25:51.258 --> 25:54.594
<i>Then this is your meat locker.</i>

25:59.474 --> 26:01.393
<i>All that...</i>

26:01.434 --> 26:03.687
<i>is dirty?</i>

26:11.987 --> 26:14.281
<i>[door opens]</i>

26:14.281 --> 26:16.283
<i>[door closes]</i>

26:20.328 --> 26:22.539
<i>Got those books you asked for.</i>

26:22.581 --> 26:25.208
<i>Also a bunch of stuff from</i>
<i>the office for you to look over.</i>

26:25.250 --> 26:28.169
<i>You handle it. Better for</i>
<i>your development that way.</i>

26:28.211 --> 26:29.296
<i>Uh-huh.</i>

26:29.296 --> 26:30.672
<i>-I think I'm developed.</i>
<i>-Hmm. [chuckles]</i>

26:30.714 --> 26:33.300
<i>The line troops would</i>
<i>love to hear from you.</i>

26:33.300 --> 26:34.551
<i>Whenever your sabbatical--</i>

26:34.593 --> 26:36.344
<i>Nope, not a sabbatical.</i>

26:36.386 --> 26:38.346
<i>This clean air gets</i>
<i>a person thinking.</i>

26:38.346 --> 26:40.890
<i>-That's what I'm doing.</i>
<i>-Okay.</i>

26:40.890 --> 26:43.351
<i>I will handle</i>
<i>the work stuff while you think.</i>

26:43.393 --> 26:44.769
<i>How long do you imagine--</i>

26:44.811 --> 26:47.606
<i>Until I figure out how</i>
<i>to actually get something done</i>

26:47.606 --> 26:50.650
<i>from that chair behind my desk.</i>

26:50.692 --> 26:52.110
<i>You've known me a long time,</i>

26:52.110 --> 26:54.070
<i>and you know</i>
<i>I don't shy from battle.</i>

26:54.070 --> 26:55.822
<i>But pointless battle?</i>

26:55.822 --> 26:56.781
<i>It's not my jam.</i>

26:56.781 --> 26:59.075
<i>Neither is losing,</i>
<i>being thwarted,</i>

26:59.075 --> 27:00.535
<i>or spitting into the wind.</i>

27:00.535 --> 27:01.745
<i>So, I'll be back</i>

27:01.786 --> 27:04.998
<i>when I see a road to victory.</i>
<i>And likely not sooner.</i>

27:08.001 --> 27:09.836
<i>-I'll get to it.</i>
<i>-No. Later.</i>

27:09.836 --> 27:12.589
<i>First you can stay</i>
<i>and have some hunter's stew.</i>

27:12.631 --> 27:14.633
<i>Nah, not in my diet.</i>

27:14.633 --> 27:16.426
<i>Have a seat, Ms. Sacker.</i>

27:16.426 --> 27:19.012
<i>You can pick</i>
<i>around the meat...</i>

27:19.054 --> 27:21.348
<i>and I could use the company.</i>

27:34.361 --> 27:36.279
<i>[iron squealing]</i>

27:36.321 --> 27:39.032
<i>[mechanism groaning]</i>

27:42.077 --> 27:44.788
<i>[water rushing]</i>

28:01.888 --> 28:05.225
<i>Email just hit</i>
<i>from Melville Revere.</i>

28:05.225 --> 28:06.267
<i>I know the name.</i>

28:06.309 --> 28:08.311
<i>Investor we inherited</i>
<i>from Axe Cap.</i>

28:08.353 --> 28:09.562
<i>Oh.</i>

28:09.604 --> 28:13.692
<i>Mr. Revere's cannonballs</i>
<i>and gunpowder got wet?</i>

28:13.692 --> 28:15.652
<i>The shed where he stores</i>
<i>his ammo was flooded</i>

28:15.694 --> 28:17.445
<i>by a stream he shares</i>
<i>with a neighbor,</i>

28:17.445 --> 28:19.489
<i>so he couldn't fire off</i>
<i>his morning blast.</i>

28:19.531 --> 28:22.033
<i>Not a phrase I use often, but...</i>
<i>white people problems.</i>

28:22.033 --> 28:24.536
<i>Truly. And why does he</i>
<i>think our little depository</i>

28:24.577 --> 28:26.454
<i>can help with this</i>
<i>particular problem?</i>

28:26.496 --> 28:27.706
<i>His neighbor</i>
<i>is Chuck Rhoades.</i>

28:27.706 --> 28:29.749
<i>Revere thinks</i>
<i>Rhoades flooded him.</i>

28:29.749 --> 28:31.501
<i>And he knows Wendy works here.</i>

28:31.543 --> 28:33.712
<i>He thought the ex-wife</i>
<i>would step in?</i>

28:33.712 --> 28:34.921
<i>Talk sense into Chuck?</i>

28:34.921 --> 28:36.715
<i>He thought that since</i>
<i>we manage his money,</i>

28:36.756 --> 28:38.425
<i>there might be incentive</i>
<i>in that direction, yes.</i>

28:38.466 --> 28:39.801
<i>Did Wendy feel</i>
<i>so incentivized?</i>

28:39.843 --> 28:42.429
<i>You know how in, like,</i>
<i>old Andy Capp cartoons</i>

28:42.429 --> 28:43.722
<i>when the character curses?</i>

28:43.722 --> 28:46.599
<i>She let out a stream of</i>
<i>pound signs and asterisks?</i>

28:46.641 --> 28:47.600
<i>And alphasands.</i>

28:47.600 --> 28:48.727
<i>What we now call the "at" sign.</i>

28:48.727 --> 28:50.019
<i>The verbal equivalent.</i>

28:50.019 --> 28:50.979
<i>Nice.</i>

28:51.020 --> 28:51.980
<i>Here's the not-nice.</i>

28:52.021 --> 28:54.357
<i>We have to help Revere</i>
<i>deal with Chuck Rhoades.</i>

28:54.399 --> 28:56.025
<i>-You do.</i>
<i>-I'd rather not.</i>

28:56.025 --> 28:57.277
<i>No, of course not.</i>

28:57.277 --> 28:58.695
<i>But we need the story</i>
<i>going around that</i>

28:58.695 --> 29:00.739
<i>we are satisfying</i>
<i>our investors.</i>

29:00.780 --> 29:02.282
<i>Going the extra mile or two.</i>

29:02.282 --> 29:03.450
<i>Now is the opportunity for us</i>

29:03.450 --> 29:05.243
<i>to get positive</i>
<i>word of mouth flowing.</i>

29:05.285 --> 29:06.161
<i>I'd do it, but...</i>

29:06.202 --> 29:08.455
<i>you'll do it better.</i>

29:09.289 --> 29:11.249
<i>Alphasand.</i>

29:24.721 --> 29:28.433
<i>Look at you, out here</i>
<i>in the fenland and fields.</i>

29:32.479 --> 29:34.689
<i>So, you've become</i>
<i>a modern day Cincinnatus,</i>

29:34.689 --> 29:38.568
<i>leaving matters of</i>
<i>the state for the plow.</i>

29:38.568 --> 29:40.153
<i>I merely needed a break.</i>

29:40.195 --> 29:42.655
<i>A recharge.</i>

29:42.655 --> 29:46.993
<i>I imagine you feel there's</i>
<i>unfinished business with me.</i>

29:46.993 --> 29:48.953
<i>But I'm unlike the man</i>
<i>who came before me.</i>

29:48.953 --> 29:50.705
<i>I will never give you</i>
<i>a legal opening</i>

29:50.747 --> 29:53.333
<i>because I do not</i>
<i>break the law.</i>

29:53.333 --> 29:55.668
<i>Billionaires break</i>
<i>the laws of decency,</i>

29:55.668 --> 29:58.463
<i>even while obeying the letter.</i>

29:58.505 --> 30:02.342
<i>By definition,</i>
<i>having that much is criminal.</i>

30:03.176 --> 30:05.720
<i>A point much open to debate.</i>

30:05.762 --> 30:07.472
<i>But I can be your ally.</i>

30:09.808 --> 30:12.435
<i>I know I owe you a debt.</i>
<i>I'm aware of that.</i>

30:12.477 --> 30:14.604
<i>But you should be aware</i>
<i>that I am good,</i>

30:14.604 --> 30:17.816
<i>very good,</i>
<i>at settling scores.</i>

30:17.816 --> 30:19.734
<i>And what have you come to ask,</i>

30:19.734 --> 30:22.195
<i>in order to deepen that debt?</i>

30:23.571 --> 30:25.907
<i>Melville Revere.</i>

30:25.949 --> 30:27.408
<i>Oof.</i>

30:27.408 --> 30:29.619
<i>Disagreeable sort.</i>

30:29.661 --> 30:32.121
<i>Entitled in a way</i>
<i>I've long tolerated,</i>

30:32.121 --> 30:33.289
<i>but no longer can.</i>

30:33.289 --> 30:34.958
<i>All the same,</i>
<i>I'd appreciate it</i>

30:34.999 --> 30:37.043
<i>if you left him alone,</i>
<i>spared him further harassment.</i>

30:37.043 --> 30:38.711
<i>He's a Michael Prince</i>
<i>Capital investor,</i>

30:38.753 --> 30:40.672
<i>and as such,</i>
<i>I'd hate to see him in court</i>

30:40.672 --> 30:42.465
<i>on the other end</i>
<i>of one of your actions.</i>

30:42.465 --> 30:44.342
<i>Wouldn't look</i>
<i>good for you or me.</i>

30:44.342 --> 30:46.469
<i>Why not good for me,</i>
<i>Michael?</i>

30:46.469 --> 30:48.596
<i>I mean, you'd be coming</i>
<i>after a place that manages</i>

30:48.638 --> 30:49.848
<i>your father's money.</i>

30:49.889 --> 30:51.015
<i>Good chunk of it, anyway.</i>

30:51.057 --> 30:54.394
<i>He left it</i>
<i>in after Axelrod took off.</i>

30:56.354 --> 30:57.480
<i>[chuckles]</i>

30:57.480 --> 30:58.648
<i>But, sure, worse for me.</i>

30:58.690 --> 31:03.111
<i>Because when it comes</i>
<i>to Michael Prince Capital,</i>

31:03.152 --> 31:05.363
<i>I need it to be--</i>

31:05.405 --> 31:06.865
<i>I need to be</i>

31:06.865 --> 31:09.409
<i>reputationally pristine.</i>

31:09.409 --> 31:12.203
<i>[cannons firing]</i>

31:17.584 --> 31:20.336
<i>[cannons continue firing]</i>

31:21.588 --> 31:25.884
<i>I find myself</i>
<i>unwilling to help you.</i>

31:25.925 --> 31:29.387
<i>And when it comes</i>
<i>to your client, Revere...</i>

31:29.888 --> 31:31.472
<i>you hold his money,</i>

31:31.514 --> 31:33.933
<i>you hold the whole bag.</i>

31:36.102 --> 31:38.813
<i>It's not Cincinnatus you're</i>
<i>fashioning yourself after,</i>

31:38.855 --> 31:39.981
<i>I get that now.</i>

31:40.023 --> 31:41.900
<i>It's more</i>
<i>Manius Curius Dentatus.</i>

31:41.941 --> 31:44.819
<i>"I see no glory</i>
<i>in having money myself,</i>

31:44.861 --> 31:47.697
<i>but in commanding</i>
<i>those that do."</i>

31:47.739 --> 31:50.450
<i>[sighs]</i>

31:51.701 --> 31:54.287
<i>I'm less interested</i>
<i>in speaking Latin</i>

31:54.329 --> 31:56.289
<i>than in speaking the truth.</i>

31:58.583 --> 32:00.460
<i>Safe travels.</i>

32:02.587 --> 32:05.506
<i>[Senior panting]</i>

32:05.548 --> 32:06.716
<i>You outta breath?</i>

32:06.758 --> 32:08.843
<i>Walking and talking.</i>

32:08.885 --> 32:11.304
<i>[slowly] Walking...</i>

32:11.346 --> 32:13.806
<i>and talking.</i>

32:13.848 --> 32:15.266
<i>Rolling calls.</i>

32:15.266 --> 32:16.351
<i>[scoffs]</i>

32:16.392 --> 32:17.894
<i>What do you want, Sonny?</i>

32:17.936 --> 32:19.437
<i>Who are you talking to?</i>

32:19.479 --> 32:20.605
<i>You, Sonny.</i>

