<i>Look it up!</i>

42:23.040 --> 42:25.543
<i>Just having</i>
<i>a team-building exercise.</i>

42:25.584 --> 42:29.421
<i>Ready to start rowing in</i>
<i>the same fucking direction, sir.</i>

