<i>the next update.</i>

42:44.186 --> 42:46.230
<i>'Bout fucking time</i>
<i>someone showed</i>

42:46.230 --> 42:48.107
<i>some clankers around here.</i>

42:48.148 --> 42:49.733
<i>I'd like to welcome</i>
<i>all of you,</i>

