42:56.240 --> 42:59.368
<i>One of the things I brought</i>
<i>to our organization</i>

42:59.368 --> 43:01.036
<i>is a moral barometer.</i>

43:01.078 --> 43:02.913
<i>I understand that</i>
<i>these employees</i>

