44:08.812 --> 44:11.815
<i>Let's look at</i>
<i>the prevailing winds.</i>

44:14.985 --> 44:18.947
<i>The prevailing feeling</i>
<i>in the country about wealth.</i>

44:19.698 --> 44:21.950
<i>I think it's largely right.</i>

44:21.950 --> 44:23.494
<i>Too much is concentrated</i>

44:23.494 --> 44:25.454
<i>in the hands of too few.</i>

44:25.454 --> 44:27.456
<i>But let's not blame</i>
<i>those who manage</i>

44:27.456 --> 44:28.791
<i>that wealth for them.</i>

44:28.832 --> 44:31.669
<i>Let's instead look</i>
<i>to those who profit the most.</i>

44:31.710 --> 44:33.629
<i>As one of them,</i>
<i>I understand the temptation</i>

44:33.671 --> 44:35.506
<i>more than almost anyone can.</i>

