<i>And it's true.</i>

44:36.757 --> 44:39.635
<i>Many of the wealthiest have</i>
<i>misused their resources.</i>

44:39.635 --> 44:42.388
<i>Many have cut corners.</i>

44:43.389 --> 44:45.265
<i>We will not.</i>

