<i>No.</i>

46:48.597 --> 46:51.975
<i>We flake off every investor</i>
<i>but one.</i>

46:52.017 --> 46:53.268
<i>This one.</i>

46:53.268 --> 46:54.937
<i>We like the</i>
<i>New York Firefighters.</i>

46:54.978 --> 46:56.939
<i>We'd like to keep</i>
<i>investing for you.</i>

46:56.939 --> 46:59.817
<i>Well, it's our</i>
<i>pleasure to stay.</i>

47:03.737 --> 47:06.156
<i>I'll let the rest of you</i>
<i>head on out.</i>

47:13.622 --> 47:16.625
<i>He's never leaned into</i>
<i>corner-cutting or dirty edge.</i>

47:16.625 --> 47:18.794
<i>He's resisted it, in fact.</i>

47:18.794 --> 47:20.128
<i>So he will ride with us,</i>

47:20.170 --> 47:23.340
<i>and we will rewrite the way</i>
<i>this industry works.</i>

47:23.340 --> 47:26.844
<i>And I'll need all of you</i>
<i>to help me do it.</i>

47:26.885 --> 47:29.513
<i>And we'll do it together.</i>

47:29.555 --> 47:31.557
<i>Oh, and so you know, if you</i>
<i>continue wearing your rings,</i>

47:31.557 --> 47:35.519
<i>the data will be available</i>
<i>only to you.</i>

47:35.519 --> 47:38.438
<i>It may feel like we just cut</i>
<i>our capital by two-thirds,</i>

47:38.438 --> 47:39.898
<i>but, remember,</i>

47:39.898 --> 47:42.150
<i>the one thing billionaires hate</i>

47:42.150 --> 47:44.111
<i>is being left out.</i>

47:44.152 --> 47:46.071
<i>Excluded.</i>

47:46.113 --> 47:47.281
<i>So sit back</i>

47:47.281 --> 47:51.076
<i>and watch how badly people</i>
<i>want to get on the Prince List.</i>

48:00.335 --> 48:01.587
<i>Ballsy fucking move!</i>

