50:21.643 --> 50:25.397
<i>with the pathetic laws</i>
<i>at my disposal.</i>

50:30.152 --> 50:32.529
<i>Oh, and you all</i>
<i>be sure to drop by</i>

50:32.529 --> 50:34.614
